ation bar, taking into account the mobile dropdown requirements. It seems wrapping the navigation links and buttons will make styling easier. I will include a detailed HTML block.\n\n\n**Generating Mobile Menu Code**\n\n\\n\\n\nI'm now making final adjustments to the CSS and JS to ensure the dropdown menu functions correctly on smaller screens. I am verifying the responsiveness of the menu. I'll make sure the menu elements transition smoothly, and the toggle functionality works as intended.\n\n\n","agentMetadata":{"coderAgent":{"kind":""},"model":""},"modelDisplayName":"3.1 Pro Preview","modelID":"chat-gemini-3-1-pro-preview-paid-tier"}],"threadId":"ec245a14-3317-11f1-89cb-c6de5e15f6c7"}
